<div class="section">
    <h1>Genio for Logistics</h1>
    <p class="lead">From warehouse floor to last‑mile doorstep, Genio creates a living intelligence loop that drives on‑time, in‑full performance.</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>Industry Context</h2>
    <div class="box">
        <p>Global supply chains move at the speed of expectation—yet data silos slow every handoff. TMS feeds, telematics streams, WMS events, and ERP orders speak different languages. The result: blind spots, OTIF penalties, and rising carbon scrutiny.</p>
        <p><strong>Genio Logistics</strong> unifies these signals into a recursive memory engine, giving operators, planners, and executives one continuously updating narrative of movement and risk.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>The Genio Logistics Loop</h2>
    <div class="box">
        <h3>NOW → EXPRESS</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Consumes EDI/API feeds from TMS, GPS/IoT telematics, WMS scans, yard sensors, and customer order portals in real‑time.</li>
            <li>Auto‑harmonizes SKUs, locations, and time zones across partners.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>INTERPRET → REFLECT</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Detects route deviations, dwell inflation, and temperature excursions using anomaly models.</li>
            <li>Correlates weather, port congestion, and driver HOS to forecast service risk.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>VISUALIZE → EMBED</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Streams dynamic ETA updates, cost‑to‑serve heatmaps, and carbon dashboards to control towers.</li>
            <li>Embeds every milestone as a vector for semantic search across lanes and SKUs.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>REPLAY</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Instant playback of any shipment journey—proof for customers, auditors, and continuous improvement teams.</li>
            <li>Feeds root‑cause learnings into future tendering, load planning, and network design.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Focused Modules</h2>
    <div class="box">
        <h3>1. Fleet Intelligence</h3>
        <p>Integrates engine diagnostics, driver behavior, and fuel telemetry. Predictive alerts reduce breakdowns and optimize maintenance windows—cutting downtime and emissions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
        <h3>2. Warehouse Vision</h3>
        <p>Computer‑vision feeds from dock doors track pallet flow and dwell. Genio flags bottlenecks, guiding task interleaving to lift throughput without extra headcount.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
        <h3>3. Cold Chain Assurance</h3>
        <p>Captures real‑time temperature/humidity probes. Autonomously suggests reroutes or cross‑docks to protect product integrity and service levels.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
        <h3>4. Sustainability Ledger</h3>
        <p>Aggregates fuel burn, idle time, and mode splits. Calculates shipment‑level CO<sub>2</sub>e, auto‑populating ESG disclosures and carbon marketplace offsets.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Architecture Snapshot</h2>
    <div class="box">
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Edge Ingest:</strong> REST/EDI gateways + MQTT brokers feed Apache Kafka topics.</li>
            <li><strong>Stream OPS:</strong> Flink joins events with geo‑fences and SLA rules in milliseconds.</li>
            <li><strong>Genio Heads:</strong> NER (SKU &amp; lane extraction), Sentiment (driver notes), QA, Embed—all containerized with NeMo 2.0 and deployable on GPUs, TPUs, LPUs.</li>
            <li><strong>Memory Layer:</strong> Postgres (events), Qdrant (vectors), DuckDB (time‑series) for instant replay and analytics.</li>
            <li><strong>Visualization:</strong> Mapbox GL lane viewer, Plotly KPI boards, with XR plugs for digital twins of distribution centers.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Case Study: Coast‑to‑Coast 3PL</h2>
    <div class="box">
        <p><span class="subtle">2025 – North America Network</span><br>
        A national third‑party logistics provider connected 1,200 trucks and 9 regional DCs to Genio. Within 90 days:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>OTIF performance improved from 93% to 97.5% across top retail accounts.</li>
            <li>Empty miles reduced by 11% via backhaul recommendations.</li>
            <li>Carbon reporting automated—cutting annual compliance labor by 800 hours.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Why Genio for Logistics?</h2>
    <div class="box">
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Total Visibility:</strong> One memory stream for every move and exception.</li>
            <li><strong>Speed to Action:</strong> Alerts land before costs balloon.</li>
            <li><strong>Seamless Fit:</strong> Works with your TMS, WMS, ERP—no rip‑and‑replace.</li>
            <li><strong>Future Proof:</strong> Vendor‑agnostic across clouds and compute.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

